{"tid":1069347,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"謝霆鋒將與甄子丹對打, 「實牙實齒埋身肉搏」","createTime":"2019-03-20T02:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T05:55:40.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a2126b1d2e4678320cddb6dd475f615c6d1d05ef","tid":1069347,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"西媒話謝霆鋒今次係做反派, 挑戰甄子丹 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20190320/s00016/1553019975892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Farticle%2F20190320%2Fs00016%2F1553019975892&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9DQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=f06e9a22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Farticle%2F20190320%2Fs00016%2F1553019975892&h=690a471d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20190320/s00016/1553019975892</a><br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒將主演陳木勝執導的《怒火》，繼2006年《龍虎門》後再與「宇宙最強」甄子丹合演，他期待與甄子丹對打。<br />\n....<br />\n《怒火》預告片是一個被焚燒中的人，陳木勝解釋每個人心中都有團怒火，警察和匪徒都有怒火，電影是部較火爆的警匪片。霆鋒表示被劇本觸動決定接拍，他與陳木勝合作過多部戲。電影下月開拍，陳木勝說預備好多高難度動作給霆鋒，難度在於角色和打鬥場面，演繹會與以前不同。<br />\n<br />\n「實牙實齒埋身肉搏」<br />\n<br />\n霆鋒說：「角色是新嘗試、新挑戰，香港動作電影很久沒實牙實齒、埋身肉搏，我身痕了很久。（會否擔心受傷？）<strong>拍動作片受傷是必然的，交由也是監製的甄子丹去設計，我們自10多年前拍《龍虎門》後再合作，很期待跟他對打。（可擔心甄子丹不留手？）已開始操練，看看可否打快一點。</strong>」"},{"pid":"129897330d9f94d2fea293bbb235ae394fea1055","tid":1069347,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:05:25.000Z","msg":"西媒報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/donnie-yen-joins-benny-chans-cop-thriller-raging-fire-1195572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fdonnie-yen-joins-benny-chans-cop-thriller-raging-fire-1195572&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9DQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=f5d115a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/donnie-yen-joins-benny-chans-cop-thriller-raging-fire-1195572</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEmperor announced a Donnie Yen-Benny Chan collaboration Crossfire last year at Filmart, but that project has been put on hold and Raging Fire is a new and unrelated project. Yen&rsquo;s character is a cop too honest for his own good and sees his prot&eacute;g&eacute;, played by Tse, rising in the ranks as his own career stalls. But Tse&rsquo;s unethical behavior lands him in prison, and the embittered man vows to take revenge on his former mentor."},{"pid":"1b9a93bebb1004da31fac6592db7c0f3de3c3e58","tid":1069347,"uid":38194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"唔扮廚師嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c9b2f852ca2484de6855649760be470eddb8ad","tid":1069347,"uid":236359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒返大陸就9左好多"},{"pid":"58c954242171eb93fb6d9a8a449f75b64be5935b","tid":1069347,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"Le Mon 今次會唔會真係比丹爺打撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bc902843ecfd8892568da4b46202e393d80042","tid":1069347,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"宇宙丹實就住架啦"},{"pid":"7de58fad25517dde52345edd2094daf1fe6fda4a","tid":1069347,"uid":211461,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"甄子丹做動作指導 你想打到佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衫尾都無得你掂啦 假手假腳就得<br />\n或者俾個替身你打囉 咁就點砌都得<br />\n但你放心 佢打你一定拳拳到肉"},{"pid":"2e199efb6003347550ebbe060cfa5801c8290efc","tid":1069347,"uid":74622,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"LeMon 唧糖漿隻手仲快過宇宙丹嘅日字沖拳<br />\n唔撚驚"},{"pid":"a499034771de09fae53aedab350945ae0be882ca","tid":1069347,"uid":148332,"like":4